\\ Deliberately weak model for testing abstract mechanisms.

(set *facts*
  [
    [term self-correction known]
    [term success known]
    [term improves-performance known]

    [claim c1 causal self-correction success]
    [mechanism c1 improves-performance]
    [modality c1 probable]
    [scope c1 conditional]

    [abstract improves-performance]
  ])
